Are we talking worse case here?<br>
That is a chain pulling group where the puller and chanter are queing up mobs to be killed by the rest of the group.<br>
ie no gap between targets to nuke on.<br>
<br>
In this case you casting your best nuke at the rate at which your mana regen allows.<br>
<br>
This can be easily calculated (ignoring resists)<br>
<br>
Note I am not uber...<br>
<br>
Ice Spear is my most effiecent nuke. ( Aside from bane spells)<br>
Ice Spear is 1200 hps for 300 mana<br>
I have ID3 (+10% avg) for damage adustment.<br>
and Evoc Specialisation 200 (-10%) MP3 focus (-5% avg) and scm1 (-2.5%) for mana adjustment<br>
<br>
This makes Ice Spear 1320 avg hps damage for 247 avg mana<br>
Now my standing mana regen rate is 30 (with KEI) per tick<br>
note 30 = 1 (standing) + 1 (FT 1 item) + 2 (mc2) + 4 (greater flappy) + 3 (epic) + 14 (KEI) + 5 (harvest avg)<br>
Assuming I never sat down (bare with me here...)<br>
I can cast an Ice Spear every 49.5 secs.<br>
The dps from this is 1320/49.5 or ... ~26.7 hp/s<br>
<br>
If I am on a horse I gain mana at the sitting mana rate.<br>
Thats 54 mana per tick<br>
I can cast an Ice Spear every 27.5 secs.<br>
That works out to ~48 hp/s<br>
<br>
Now the real rate with out a horse will be in beween 26.7 hp/s and 48 hp/s. It depends on how long I stand up for.<br>
I must be standing for at least the 4 secs it takes to cast Ice Spear.<br>
<br>
As it happens I have a right click nuke. 400 hps with a 13 sec cast. So while I am on my horse waiting the 27.5 secs to regen the mana for an Ice Spear I can right click nuke twice.<br>
That means 1320 + 800 hps per 27.5 secs or 77 dps<br>
<br>
The burst rate really depends on how fast other people are gaining aggro. Its aggro limited and has nothing to do with mana regen. Damage focus and crits do matter.<br>
<br>
In an typical xp group the highest burst rate dps can be calculated assuming you have inifinite mana (well FM and bursting dps until you hit oom) and are chaining the best nuke (based on damage vs casting time) alternating with concussion.<br>
One concussion will wipe about ~ 1000 dmg<br>
<br>
The best nukes from what I can tell, allowing for the casting of concussion to fully clear aggro, are the new PoP Draughts.<br>
They are 950 (1045 with ID4) every 3 secs followed by a 2 sec concussion. ie 1045 every 5 secs.<br>
Thats a dsp of  209 hp/s however it will be lower than that because of the server / client update time delaying the speed at which you can hit the spell gems.<br>
To sustain that rate however you would need to gain ~230 mana every 5 secs ie ~276 mana per tick<br>
<br>
